Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.51,0:16:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊邪那美的攻擊…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:16:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝福者！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有趣的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:14.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:33.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奈前輩 請脫離！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用同步來同化駕駛員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.52,0:17:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同化促進劑 1號到3號 給藥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同步狀態 強制解除
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.97,0:18:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們隔絕了我的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你還和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 停下 停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.71,0:18:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 大家快躲開…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.28,0:18:48.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬里爾 認證代碼確認
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.04,0:18:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}9 8 7 6 5 4 3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奈前輩 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.85,0:18:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里奈前輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 暉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然想消除自己？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招吧 祝福者！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.03,0:19:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 被他們爭取到時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不快點總士他們就要被帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:05.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你快去 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算能起飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是多虧了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.47,0:20:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感謝你 馬里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.51,0:20:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是多虧了你才能離開那個島
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.32,0:20:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實你很恨我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.01,0:20:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你將創造的世界是寄予期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普羅米修斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是人類給我起的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.60,0:20:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:44.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們叫我尊者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.50,0:20:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「海神的尊者」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:48.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後我該怎麼叫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪列斯佩羅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我給人類的最後一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道是什麼意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:58.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「絕望」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:58.62,tips,NTP,0,0,0,,註：世界語中「絕望」發音為「瑪列斯佩羅」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很值得期待吧 馬里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別走！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬里斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.44,0:21:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別逼我開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.79,0:21:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你下不了手的 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是預測了未來 才帶上我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.22,0:23:04.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機體被搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.95,0:23:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎不會不見的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他的心會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.10,0:23:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他會不再覺得天空美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.76,0:23:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在往後的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣或許更好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.69,0:24:08.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普羅米修斯Mir在大氣層外形成了極大的領域
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.52,0:24:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和海神島的內核…所預言的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.16,0:24:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行動失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.91,0:24:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探討一下該如何挽回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.07,0:24:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否則 世界和我們的故鄉都會毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.77,0:24:59.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能感覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.31,0:25:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常大的力量升上了天空
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.17,0:25:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要做好準備
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.93,0:25:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使我們的未來在今後的未來中不被毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.80,0:25:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 露維·卡瑪大人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.76,0:25:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望並沒有消失
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.06,0:25:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要悲傷 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.43,0:25:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.40,0:25:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.23,0:25:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在和平的地方生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.47,0:25:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拋棄那個
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.80,0:25:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犧牲一些人來讓另一些人活下去的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.43,0:25:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.87,0:26:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,80,,{\fnMingLiU\fs60\shad2\bord0\fad(800,800)\4c&H000000&}—— 三 年 後 ——
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.80,0:26:35.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.10,0:26:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對面有些什麼呢
